## Letter Proportion Function
```{r}
letterProportion <- function(string){
  lstring <- tolower(string)
  letters <- unlist(strsplit(lstring,NULL))
  letters2 <- letters[letters %in% c()]
}

letterProportionOutput <- letterProportion()
```
## Frequence Compare Function
```{r}
freqCompare <- function(letterProportionOutput,English){
  alpha <- (English)
  if length(letterProportionOutput)==0
  for (in alpha)
}
```
